I have gotten root canal treatment done by Dr. Snigdha mam and she is soo sweet and professional. Definitely would recommend her to everyone I know.
Shez friendly in nature, listens to all my queries and provides treatment accordingly... I recommend snigdha mam for all skin related problems.. Thank you.
Doctor should have explained the cause and the problem in simpler words which is understandable by patients rather than using complex terms.

Dr.Snigdha & Dr.Iswarya treated very well as I am suffering from teeth pain since many years. They treated the root canal without any pain.
